                <p>With fire and ice fused in the landscape, <b>Iceland is a unique adventure</b> for the traveller through that dramatic landscape and geothermal wonders, unspoiled natural beauty, erupting volcanoes, massive glaciers, hot springs, and combinations of rock and ocean; the whole island is a paradise where one can be assured that experiences will be unforgettable. Nature-loving enthusiasts, thrill-seekers, or shutterbugs, Iceland will keep its spell laying over you.</p>
